&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced Corporate Legal Specialist to join our dynamic legal team. As we continue to scale rapidly, we need a detail-oriented legal operations partner who can provide crucial support across our corporate legal functions. The ideal candidate will bring substantial transactional experience and demonstrated ability to build and operationalize corporate processes, particularly around operationalizing corporate policies, record management, and system integrations.&lt;/p&gt;
